			"body": "<!-- This is an auto-generated comment: summarize by coderabbit.ai -->\n<!-- walkthrough_start -->\n\n<details>\n<summary>📝 Walkthrough</summary>\n\n## Walkthrough\n\nTheme support has been added to the emoji picker in the folder dialog component. The parent component now forwards its theme ID to the IconSelector, which applies the theme to ensure the emoji picker respects the user's selected theme setting.\n\n## Changes\n\n|Cohort / File(s)|Summary|\n|---|---|\n|**Emoji Picker Theme Support** <br> `packages/app-desktop/gui/EditFolderDialog/Dialog.tsx`, `packages/app-desktop/gui/EditFolderDialog/IconSelector.tsx`|Added `themeId` prop propagation from Dialog to IconSelector. IconSelector now computes a picker theme via `useMemo` using `themeStyle(themeId)` and applies it to the EmojiButton to ensure emoji picker respects the user's selected theme.|\n\n## Estimated code review effort\n\n🎯 3 (Moderate) | ⏱️ ~20 minutes\n\n## Poem\n\n> 🐰 The emoji picker wears dark robes with pride,\n> No longer in daylight does it try to hide,\n> When darkness falls soft across the screen,\n> Our folder selections wear the theme pristine! 🌙✨\n\n</details>\n\n<!-- walkthrough_end -->\n\n\n<!-- pre_merge_checks_walkthrough_start -->\n\n<details>\n<summary>🚥 Pre-merge checks | ✅ 4 | ❌ 1</summary>\n\n<details>\n<summary>❌ Failed checks (1 warning)</summary>\n\n|     Check name     | Status     | Explanation                                                                          | Resolution                                                                         |\n| :----------------: | :--------- | :----------------------------------------------------------------------------------- | :--------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |\n| Docstring Coverage | ⚠️ Warning | Docstring coverage is 0.00% which is insufficient. The required threshold is 80.00%. | Write docstrings for the functions missing them to satisfy the coverage threshold. |\n\n</details>\n<details>\n<summary>✅ Passed checks (4 passed)</summary>\n\n|         Check name         | Status   | Explanation                                                                                                                                                                                              |\n| :------------------------: | :------- | :------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |\n|      Description Check     | ✅ Passed | Check skipped - CodeRabbit’s high-level summary is enabled.                                                                                                                                              |\n|         Title check        | ✅ Passed | The title accurately describes the main change: adding an argument to the emoji picker for automatic theme-based switching, directly addressing issue `#14080`.                                            |\n|     Linked Issues check    | ✅ Passed | The code changes implement the required functionality from `#14080` by adding themeId prop forwarding and computing pickerTheme via useMemo to ensure emoji picker respects system/application dark theme. |\n| Out of Scope Changes check | ✅ Passed | All changes are directly related to the objective of adding theming support to the emoji picker; no unrelated or out-of-scope modifications are present.                                                 |\n\n</details>\n\n<sub>✏️ Tip: You can configure your own custom pre-merge checks in the settings.</sub>\n\n</details>\n\n<!-- pre_merge_checks_walkthrough_end -->\n\n<!-- finishing_touch_checkbox_start -->\n\n<details>\n<summary>✨ Finishing touches</summary>\n\n- [ ] <!-- {\"checkboxId\": \"7962f53c-55bc-4827-bfbf-6a18da830691\"} --> 📝 Generate docstrings\n<details>\n<summary>🧪 Generate unit tests (beta)</summary>\n\n- [ ] <!-- {\"checkboxId\": 